snippet.title: Beyond All Reason | Massive GFX Update | Q4 2022
snippet.description:
Over 9 months of hard work has been put into this massive GFX update for BAR / Beyond All Reason RTS. Proud to announce 2 new systems that will be on by default, and another one that can be enabled manually.

• New Lighting System
• New Decal System
• New Volumetric Fog

Check out BAR on https://www.beyondallreason.info/
Read the full details on this GFX update and more news here: https://www.beyondallreason.info/news/a-revolution-in-bar-graphics-remastered-textures-effects-and-lighting
Or join our Discord here: https://discord.gg/N968ddE

Music by Ryan Krause
https://linktr.ee/ryankrause
